## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the latest industry trends or unpublished strategies employed by emerging platform leaders. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources, potentially excluding relevant insights from non-English publications. Furthermore, the dynamic nature of platform leadership means that strategies can evolve rapidly, and this report may not reflect the most current practices.